Class GoogleOauth2CallbackServlet

java.lang.Object
  javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
          org.lantern.http.GoogleOauth2CallbackServlet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig
public class GoogleOauth2CallbackServlet
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet

Servlet for handling OAuth callbacks from Google. The associated code is converted into OAuth tokens that are used to login to Google Talk and to obtain any other necessary data.
